/>\n我一分鐘屌你老母50次你頂唔頂得順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050c96bf154c782f9b4791f4dee813012432b87e","tid":424121,"uid":62289,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"個從從 被人屌完 之後自己直播 呢下<br />\n好似d濕鳩港女呃like 咁 <br />\n好撚小家 <br />\n你一係當面屌返人 <br />\n一係開記者會"},{"pid":"3ad181434a0d7b4292ca444fc8696aa4e03b24c2","tid":424121,"uid":119778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"半夜直播痛哭喊告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea8019c547a84563a721586ea184c4d1b2842a4","tid":424121,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開頭係一面倒撐佢，<br />\n衰在開直播喊苦喊忽仲要話告人，<br />\n乃哥錯在唔好老脾亂屌老母，<br />\n從從衰在戇鳩，得理不饒人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">睇到佢個直播真係搖哂頭覺得呢步好錯。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心佢叫個記者扮偷影到佢對住老母失聲痛哭仲好啦<br />\n<br />\n直播真係多此一舉，明顯睇到網上風聲以為自己win硬"},{"pid":"28143c85d7d387b984f273e6a467ff7c7e9870e9","tid":424121,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半夜直播痛哭喊告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想圍爐取暖結果俾人笑冇賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f1776e39c9cbb37b43741ec2d646e38d261e87","tid":424121,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"乃哥個節目真心好睇<br />\n<br />\n連樓上咁支持嘅曾掌門都比人發現佢抄沖沖沖D GAME...<br />\n<br />\n比人爆仲要死兜無抄人<br />\n<br />\n真係好有大哥風範喎"},{"pid":"21f30a7b5a158da18eb360152c6f28771e2a74af","tid":424121,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"直播好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5202a1d0224b9204d1cbad23b6b6cfc57fa545","tid":424121,"uid":67509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乃哥個節目真心好睇<br />\n<br />\n連樓上咁支持嘅曾掌門都比人發現佢抄沖沖沖D GAME...<br />\n<br />\n比人爆仲要死兜無抄人<br />\n<br />\n真係好有大哥風範喎</blockquote><br />\n跳跳tempo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5569679bb79228a966f73a8dcbbb1a11eab777f","tid":424121,"uid":93202,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦<br />\n根本個從從平時做節目都唔受工作人員歡迎<br />\n睇多少少台綜都會知 <br />\n啲綜藝節目總有一兩集係有爆料<br />\n或者直接搵工作人員黎投票 康熙都有搞過<br />\n根本條友就有問題, 自以為大佬<br />\n只係今次串着個比佢更大粒嘅 咪有位博同情囉"},{"pid":"2e7fb753b0e31bc20fc377662c5a549911efe7b2","tid":424121,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>從從都傻嘅<br />\n台灣演藝圈最講輩份<br />\n大哥就算有錯<br />\n佢咁樣jer住哂博同情<br />\n其他人應該都覺得過左火</blockquote><br />\n台灣比較上黎算係最唔講輩份啦喎<br />\n好多藝人成日當住佢地面抽水佢地都無野</blockquote><br />\n睇咩節目啦<br />\n同埋其實都好講輩份架<br />\n只係有啲醒目仔抽水唔會抽盡<br />\n仲識補救/話係節目效果<br />\n蠢果啲咪比人玩死都唔知咩事<br />\n咁岩呢件事2個都柒<br />\n徐乃就成日無料扮大袋<br />\n睇下隔離國光孫鵬日日撚狗永遠無人敢駁(利申好憎孫鵬)<br />\n仲要鵬哥前鵬哥後<br />\n個從從就撈呢行咁多年都彈唔起就知又係無料<br />\n兩件垃圾互鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好憎條粉腸 不過孫鵬起碼知自己廢先<br />\n睇左咁耐最勁都係憲哥 華人界無人能及</blockquote><br />\n你當張菲流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張飛唔係流，但憲哥係前無古人 後無來者</blockquote><br />\n乜方面無人能及先"}]}